Official Campsite
Categories
The race is open to all levels of fitness, with a category to suit athletes, leisure runners and walkers alike, with the overall aim of ensuring a fun and friendly atmosphere. Medals will be given to all finishers. Individuals or teams of 3 or 4 people are welcome.
There is also an award for anyone who can beat the best finishing times:
Men: 35.34 mins (Martin Lyons 2010),
Women:45.07 (Rachel Mannion 2010).
                           Teams:

Why not get your workmates or friends together and race against other local businesses and organisations. Teams can be made up of 3 people. All three members run the full distance and the winning team is the one with the lowest average.
First team get a perpetual shield as well as an individual trophy for each team member to keep. Trophies for 2nd and 3rd team as well as 1st Club team across the line.
€25/team
